<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Chip-Seq on</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/categories/chip-seq/</link><description>Recent content in Chip-Seq on</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 21 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/categories/chip-seq/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>ChIP-seq 전처리 (trimmomatic, samtools)</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/bioinformatics/bi5/</link><pubDate>Mon, 21 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/bioinformatics/bi5/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="chip-seq-전처리-trimmomatic-samtools"&gt;
 ChIP-seq 전처리 (trimmomatic, samtools)
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#chip-seq-%ec%a0%84%ec%b2%98%eb%a6%ac-trimmomatic-samtools"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
